text.tspan: Step 2. Provide intent to Accept Waiver and Code of Conduct
Can now volunteer with FreeGeek Chicago

flowRoot.flowPara: Profile should be created with NO Orientation of Signed Waiver date.
Orientation Date can be filled in automatically during a special self-sign-up session (e.g. Online registration during orientation) OR manually on this screen.
Signed Waiver Date can be filled in automatically by an admin after printing waivers OR manually on this screen.
